  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Orphan works and cultural heritage institutions: copyright after the transition period
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Cultural heritage institutions will not be able to rely on the orphan works exception after the end of the transition period.</p>

  </div>
</div>

